# 🎬 AI Sage Video Generator

Ancient Indian Sage style talking videos — bilkul YouTube Shorts jaisi!

**Topic likho → AI Script → AI Voice → Talking Video → Download!**

---

## 🚀 Quick Setup (15 minutes mein done!)

### Step 1 — GitHub pe Upload Karo

1. [github.com](https://github.com) pe jaao → New Repository
2. Name: `ai-video-generator`
3. Public rakho
4. Ye 3 files upload karo:
   - `app.py`
   - `requirements.txt`
   - `README.md`

---

### Step 2 — Streamlit Cloud pe Deploy Karo (FREE)

1. [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io) pe jaao
2. GitHub se login karo
3. "New App" click karo
4. Apna repo select karo → `app.py` select karo
5. **Deploy!** → App live ho jayegi!

---

### Step 3 — API Keys Banao (Sab FREE)

#### 🤖 Anthropic API (Script Generation)
1. [console.anthropic.com](https://console.anthropic.com) → Signup
2. API Keys → Create Key
3. `sk-ant-...` wali key copy karo

#### 🔊 ElevenLabs (Voice Generation)
1. [elevenlabs.io](https://elevenlabs.io) → Free Signup
2. Profile → API Key copy karo
3. Free mein 10,000 characters/month milte hain

#### 🎥 D-ID (Talking Video)
1. [studio.d-id.com](https://studio.d-id.com) → Free Signup
2. Settings → API Keys → Generate
3. Free mein 5 minutes of video/month milta hai

#### 🖼️ Leonardo AI (Character Images)
1. [app.leonardo.ai](https://app.leonardo.ai) → Free Signup
2. Image generate karo
3. Image pe right-click → "Copy Image Address"

---

### Step 4 — Character Image Banao (Leonardo AI)

**Ye prompt use karo:**
```
Ancient Indian rishi sage, muscular warrior saint, long black hair tied up,
rudraksha beads necklace, white dhoti, tilak on forehead, sitting in ancient
hut, wooden tools visible, warm dramatic lighting, cinematic 4K portrait,
ultra realistic, Story of Great Souls style
```

