## 🆘 Common Problems

**Script generate nahi ho raha?**
→ Anthropic key check karo, balance check karo

**Voice error aa raha hai?**
→ ElevenLabs pe free quota check karo

**Video nahi ban raha?**
→ Image URL direct accessible hona chahiye (Google Drive links kaam nahi karenge)
→ D-ID pe sign in karke manually bhi bana sakte ho

